This item tracks Confirmed Kills.

Flip knives sport a Persian-style back-swept blade with an acute point. While the point itself may be fragile, the overall design of the flip knife's design is surprisingly durable. It has been spray-painted in a sun-dappled pattern.\n\nThe Phoenix is not a symbol of destruction... it's a symbol of rebirth - Valeria Jenner, Revolutionary
